snippet.title: ImageFight & XMultiply: Arcade Gears (イメージファイト＆Ｘ-マルチプライ アーケードギアーズ). [Saturn].  1CC. HARD. 60Fps.
snippet.description:
ImageFight & XMultiply: Arcade Gears (イメージファイト＆Ｘ-マルチプライ アーケードギアーズ). 1CC. HARD. 60Fps.
:- Played By PiE. - "July 4th, 2020".
.
Wiki- "a Sega Saturn compilation of two shoot-'em-up games, Image Fight and XMultiply originally released by Irem into the arcades in 1988 and 1989 respectively. It was released as art of Xing's "Arcade Gears" range exclusively in Japan. It is now considered a very rare Saturn game.".
.
